{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "file:src/aiChat.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "aiChat.js",
      "filePath": "src/aiChat.js",
      "summary": "基于本地分析结果构造情感顾问上下文，并通过 OpenRouter 的 streaming chat completions API 提供交互式问答。模块同时负责会话状态、API Key 持久化和聊天面板 DOM 更新。",
      "tags": ["ai-chat", "openrouter", "streaming", "ui-component"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "使用原生 Fetch API 读取 SSE 风格的数据流，并通过闭包维护单次页面会话状态。"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/aiChat.js:buildSystemPrompt",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "buildSystemPrompt",
      "filePath": "src/aiChat.js",
      "lineRange": [12, 71],
      "summary": "把评分、双向比例、信号分布、代表语录和画像标签压缩为中文 system prompt，作为 AI 顾问回答的事实上下文。",
      "tags": ["prompt-builder", "serialization", "analysis-context"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/aiChat.js:callLLM",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "callLLM",
      "filePath": "src/aiChat.js",
      "lineRange": [74, 140],
      "summary": "向 OpenRouter 发起流式 chat completions 请求，解析逐行 data 事件并把增量文本交给回调，同时将 HTTP 错误转换为可展示的异常。",
      "tags": ["api-client", "streaming", "error-handling", "openrouter"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/aiChat.js:initAIChat",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "initAIChat",
      "filePath": "src/aiChat.js",
      "lineRange": [143, 339],
      "summary": "初始化 AI 顾问面板、对话历史和所有输入事件，并在用户提问时驱动流式回答、错误反馈、折叠状态与 API Key 保存。",
      "tags": ["ui-initializer", "event-handler", "conversation-state", "local-storage"],
      "complexity": "complex"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:src/analyzer.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "analyzer.js",
      "filePath": "src/analyzer.js",
      "summary": "纯前端关系分析引擎，按关键词和 emoji 检测五类暧昧信号，并计算总分、等级、双方信号比例、每日开场比例、月度趋势和代表语录。输出是结果页、分享卡片和 AI 顾问共同消费的统一分析对象。",
      "tags": ["analysis-engine", "heuristic-scoring", "data-transformation", "relationship-signals"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "采用配置驱动的词典扫描与多阶段聚合，主要计算完全在浏览器内同步完成。"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/analyzer.js:generateTags",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "generateTags",
      "filePath": "src/analyzer.js",
      "lineRange": [71, 126],
      "summary": "根据总体信号密度、双方暧昧比例和最突出信号类别生成面向展示的关系画像标签。",
      "tags": ["classification", "tag-generator", "heuristic-rules"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/analyzer.js:analyze",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "analyze",
      "filePath": "src/analyzer.js",
      "lineRange": [130, 353],
      "summary": "对标准化消息执行信号匹配、加权评分和多维聚合，生成包含等级、双向对比、时间线、Top 语录及标签的完整报告。",
      "tags": ["analysis-pipeline", "scoring", "aggregation", "exported-api"],
      "complexity": "complex"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:src/cardRenderer.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "cardRenderer.js",
      "filePath": "src/cardRenderer.js",
      "summary": "把分析结果渲染为固定宽度的白底分享卡片，集中展示评分、信号分布、双向比例、代表语录和关系标签，供截图、下载或复制。",
      "tags": ["card-renderer", "dom-rendering", "share-output", "visualization"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/cardRenderer.js:renderShareCard",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "renderShareCard",
      "filePath": "src/cardRenderer.js",
      "lineRange": [11, 112],
      "summary": "将分析结果插值为完整分享卡片 HTML，包括 SVG 分数环、摘要统计、双方对比、Top 语录和标签区域。",
      "tags": ["dom-rendering", "template-generation", "share-card", "exported-api"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/cardRenderer.js:renderCardBars",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "renderCardBars",
      "filePath": "src/cardRenderer.js",
      "lineRange": [114, 137],
      "summary": "按最大信号值归一化各类别宽度，并生成分享卡片中的信号分布条形列表。",
      "tags": ["visualization", "normalization", "template-helper"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:src/main.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "main.js",
      "filePath": "src/main.js",
      "summary": "浏览器应用入口，加载全局样式，并在 DOMContentLoaded 后调用 UI 初始化函数绑定页面行为。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "bootstrap", "browser-app"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:src/parser.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "parser.js",
      "filePath": "src/parser.js",
      "summary": "接收上传的聊天 JSON，兼容数组或带 messages 字段的对象，并把多种时间、发送者、方向和内容字段归一化为分析器所需格式。另提供随机 Demo 聊天数据用于无文件体验。",
      "tags": ["parser", "normalization", "validation", "demo-data"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/parser.js:parseChatJson",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "parseChatJson",
      "filePath": "src/parser.js",
      "lineRange": [23, 59],
      "summary": "解析并验证上传的 JSON 顶层结构，标准化消息、识别参与者，并返回联系人名称与原始消息计数。",
      "tags": ["json-parser", "validation", "exported-api"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/parser.js:normalizeMessage",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "normalizeMessage",
      "filePath": "src/parser.js",
      "lineRange": [61, 104],
      "summary": "把不同导出格式中的时间戳、发送者、发送方向和文本字段映射到统一消息对象，并过滤无内容的非文本记录。",
      "tags": ["normalization", "data-mapping", "message-filter"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/parser.js:recognizeParticipants",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "recognizeParticipants",
      "filePath": "src/parser.js",
      "lineRange": [106, 133],
      "summary": "统计发送者频次并结合 isMe 标记推断本人和主要联系人，无法唯一识别时退化为消息量最多的两人。",
      "tags": ["participant-detection", "aggregation", "fallback-logic"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:src/parser.js:generateDemoData",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "generateDemoData",
      "filePath": "src/parser.js",
      "lineRange": [138, 196],
      "summary": "从预置双方话术中随机生成约一年的 300 至 499 条时间有序消息，并序列化为应用可直接导入的 JSON。",
      "tags": ["demo-data", "fixture-generator", "serialization", "exported-api"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:src/ui.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "ui.js",
      "filePath": "src/ui.js",
      "summary": "应用的浏览器编排层，连接文件导入、消息解析、关系分析、结果渲染、AI 顾问和分享卡片导出，并维护页面步骤与当前分析状态。还负责拖放、复制图片、文本降级和下载等用户交互。",
      "tags": ["ui-orchestrator", "event-handler", "dom-rendering", "export-workflow"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "以模块级状态和缓存 DOM 引用组织原生 JavaScript 单页流程，通过 html2canvas 与 Clipboard API 完成导出。"
    },
